    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-05-19T02:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-05-19T02:00:00-05:00" n="774"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d774">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.003/685: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-05-19T15:00:00+08:00"
                            >May 19, 1931—3 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received May 19—6:03 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My May 9, 11 a.m., on personal status. The second paragraph of the British text
                    should read as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“All such cases of personal status where only British subjects are
                            concerned will at the option of any of the parties concerned be dealt
                            with outside the jurisdiction of the Chinese courts.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>The British are endeavoring to have the Chinese accept the words “of any”, and I
                    suggest they be put in the American draft for discussion with C. C. Wu.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
